message.content:
Reinforcement Learning, Neural Networks. 

Reinforcement learning is present in the paper as the authors propose a reinforcement learning framework for the robot to learn control laws in local environments. The reinforcement function is generated from the sensory inputs of the robot before and after a control action is taken. 

Neural networks are also present in the paper as the authors propose that the robot learns the control law in terms of a neural network within the reinforcement learning framework.
